[SBS] Chuckster.code:
; NAME: [SBS] Chuckster
; GAMES: MP3_USA
; EXECUTION: Direct
; PARAM: Space|Destination1
; PARAM: Space|Destination2
; PARAM: Space|Destination3
; PARAM: Space|Destination4
; PARAM: Space|PrevSpace1
; PARAM: Space|PrevSpace2
; PARAM: Space|PrevSpace3
; PARAM: Space|PrevSpace4
; PARAM: Space|NextSpace1
; PARAM: Space|NextSpace2
; PARAM: Space|NextSpace3
; PARAM: Space|NextSpace4

ADDIU SP SP -80 ; Aligned by 8 to avoid N64 crash
SW RA 76(SP)
SW S0 72(SP)
SW S1 68(SP)
SW S2 64(SP)
SW S3 60(SP)
SW S4 56(SP)
SW S5 52(SP)
SW S6 48(SP)
SW S7 44(SP)

; S0 = Next Chain Index
; S1 = Next Space Index
; S2 = Destination Chain Index
; S3 = Destination Space Index
; S5 = True Space Index
; S4 = Current Player's Index
; S6 = Previous Chain Index - X Coords
; S7 = Previous Space Index - Y Coords

LOOP:
JAL GetRandomByte ; Random Int at V0
NOP

SLTI T0 V0 25
NOP
BNE T0 R0 warpstart
NOP
SLTI T0 V0 50
NOP
BNE T0 R0 warp1
NOP
SLTI T0 V0 75
NOP
BNE T0 R0 warp2
NOP
SLTI T0 V0 100
NOP
BNE T0 R0 warp3
NOP
J LOOP
NOP

warpstart:
LI S0 NextSpace4_chain_index
LI S1 NextSpace4_chain_space_index
LI S2 Destination4_chain_index
LI S3 Destination4_chain_space_index
LI S6 PrevSpace4_chain_index
LI S7 PrevSpace4_chain_space_index
J message
NOP

warp1:
LI S0 NextSpace1_chain_index
LI S1 NextSpace1_chain_space_index
LI S2 Destination1_chain_index
LI S3 Destination1_chain_space_index
LI S6 PrevSpace1_chain_index
LI S7 PrevSpace1_chain_space_index
J message
NOP

warp2:
LI S0 NextSpace2_chain_index
LI S1 NextSpace2_chain_space_index
LI S2 Destination2_chain_index
LI S3 Destination2_chain_space_index
LI S6 PrevSpace2_chain_index
LI S7 PrevSpace2_chain_space_index
J message
NOP

warp3:
LI S0 NextSpace3_chain_index
LI S1 NextSpace3_chain_space_index
LI S2 Destination3_chain_index
LI S3 Destination3_chain_space_index
LI S6 PrevSpace3_chain_index
LI S7 PrevSpace3_chain_space_index

message:
SW R0 16(SP) ; A4
SW R0 20(SP) ; A5
SW R0 24(SP) ; A6
LI A0 0x37 ; Character image (Giant Mr. Blizzard)
LUI A1 hi(Hurlster_Message)
ADDIU A1 A1 lo(Hurlster_Message)
LI A2 0 ; Param 2
JAL ShowMessage
LI A3 0 ; Param 3

JAL CloseMessage
NOP

LI A0 4 ; Happening Fadeout
JAL InitFadeOut
LI A1 16 ; 16 Frames

JAL SleepProcess
LI A0 17 ; 17 Frames

JAL GetCurrentPlayerIndex ; Player Index located at V0
NOP
MOVE S4 V0

MOVE A0 S4 ; Copy Current Player's Index to A0
JAL PlaySadVoice
NOP

JAL PlaySound
LI A0 0x3D3 ; Flying Snowball sound

; WARP --------------------------------------------------------------
MOVE A0 S4 ; Current Player Index to A0
MOVE A1 S2 ; Chain Index to A1
JAL SetPlayerOntoChain
MOVE A2 S3 ; Space Index to A2

MOVE A0 S4 ; Current Player Index to A0
MOVE A1 S0 ; Chain Index to A1
JAL SetNextChainAndSpace
MOVE A2 S1 ; Space Index to A2

MOVE A0 S4 ; Current Player Index to A0
MOVE A1 S6 ; Chain Index to A1
JAL SetPrevChainAndSpace
MOVE A2 S7 ; Space Index to A2

MOVE A0 S2 ; Destination Chain Index
JAL GetAbsSpaceIndexFromChainSpaceIndex ; True Space Index at V0
MOVE A1 S3 ; Destination Space Index

MOVE S5 V0 ; Copy True Space Index to S5

MOVE A0 S5 ; Copy True Space Index to A0
JAL SetSpaceType 
LI A1 4 ; Happening Space value 

JAL GetSpaceData ; Pointer to Space Data at V0
MOVE A0 S5

ADDIU V0 V0 8 ; This gets the X pos of the space
LW V1 0(V0) 
MOVE S6 V1 ; Copy to S6

ADDIU V0 V0 8 ; This gets the Y pos of the space
LW V1 0(V0)
MOVE S7 V1 ; Copy to S7

JAL GetPlayerStruct ; Player Struct at V0
LI A0 -1 ; Current Player

LW V1 0x24(V0) ; Load Offset 24 into V1
ADDIU V1 V1 0xC ; Add 0xC to get current player's X Coords
SW S6 0(V1) 

ADDIU V1 V1 8 ; This should load current player's Y Coords
SW S7 0(V1)
; WARP --------------------------------------------------------------

LI A0 -1 ; Current Player
LI A1 4 ; Dizzy animation
JAL SetBoardPlayerAnimation
LI A2 2 ; Loop

JAL SleepProcess ; Sleeps for 35 frames
LI A0 35

LI A0 4 ; Happening Fadeout
JAL InitFadeIn
LI A1 16 ; 16 Frames

JAL SleepProcess
LI A0 45 ; 45 Frames

MOVE A0 S5 ; Pass True Space Index to A0
JAL DeactivateHiddenBlocks
NOP


exit:
LW RA 76(SP)
LW S0 72(SP)
LW S1 68(SP)
LW S2 64(SP)
LW S3 60(SP)
LW S4 56(SP)
LW S5 52(SP)
LW S6 48(SP)
LW S7 44(SP)
JR RA
ADDIU SP SP 80



PlaySadVoice:
ADDIU SP SP -32
SW RA 28(SP)

LUI T1 hi(p1_char)
ADDIU T1 T1 lo(p1_char) ; Load Player 1's Character address
LI T0 0x38 ; Distance between each player's Character address
MULT A0 T0 ;  Multiply Current Player Index by S3
MFLO T0 ; Move the result to S3

ADDU T1 T1 T0 ; Add result to get current Player's Star address
LBU T0 0(T1) ; Load address value into S2

JAL PlaySound
MOVE A0 V0

; A0 = True Space Index

LUI T1 hi(hidden_block_star_space_index)

LB T0 0(T1) ; Load Value of Star HB Address to T0
BEQ T0 A0 movestarHB
NOP

ADDIU T1 T1 lo(hidden_block_coins_space_index)

NOP

BEQ T0 A0 moveitemHB
NOP
J DeactivateHiddenBlocks_exit
NOP

movestarHB:
LUI T2 hi(0x800CD096)
ADDIU T2 T2 lo(0x800CD096) ; Load Free RAM Address to T2
SB T0 0(T2) ; Store HB's True Space Index 
LI T0 0xFF
SB T0 0(T1) ; Removes HB from the Star HB Address
J DeactivateHiddenBlocks_exit
NOP

movecoinsHB:
LUI T2 hi(0x800CD097)
ADDIU T2 T2 lo(0x800CD097) ; Load Free RAM Address to T2
SB T0 0(T2) ; Store HB's True Space Index 
LI T0 0xFF
SB T0 0(T1) ; Removes HB from the Coins HB Address
J DeactivateHiddenBlocks_exit
NOP

moveitemHB:
LUI T2 hi(0x800CD098)
ADDIU T2 T2 lo(0x800CD098) ; Load Free RAM Address to T2
SB T0 0(T2) ; Store HB's True Space Index 
LI T0 0xFF
SB T0 0(T1) ; Removes HB from the Item HB Address

LW RA 28(SP)
JR RA
